### Configure Global Job Processing Order in Payload CMS buildConfig

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/jobs-queue/queues.mdx

This snippet demonstrates setting a global 'processingOrder' for all jobs within the Payload CMS 'buildConfig'. It uses a string value ('-createdAt') to define a LIFO (Last-In, First-Out) order based on job creation time, mimicking Payload's sort property.

```ts
export default buildConfig({
  // Other configurations...
  jobs: {
    tasks: [
      // your tasks here
    ],
    processingOrder: '-createdAt', // Process jobs in reverse order of creation = LIFO
  },
})
```

