### Payload CMS `autoRun` and `schedule` Interaction for Timing

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/jobs-queue/schedules.mdx

Explains how `schedule` queues jobs and `autoRun` executes them in Payload CMS, addressing issues where jobs run immediately instead of at their scheduled time. It emphasizes setting `autoRun` to check the queue frequently.

```typescript
// The schedule property only queues the job
// The autoRun picks it up and runs it
schedule: [{ cron: '0 0 * * *', queue: 'nightly' }]

// Make sure autoRun checks the queue frequently enough
autoRun: [
  {
    cron: '* * * * *', // Check every minute
    queue: 'nightly',
  },
]

```

