### Configure a Date Field in Payload CMS (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/fields/date.mdx

This snippet illustrates how to define a Date field within a Payload CMS field configuration. By setting the `type` property to `date`, you enable date storage and integrate a customizable time picker in the Admin Panel. This requires importing the `Field` type from 'payload'.

```typescript
import type { Field } from 'payload'

export const MyDateField: Field = {
  // ...
  type: 'date' // highlight-line
}
```

