### Increase Payload CMS `autoRun` Frequency for Faster Job Execution

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/jobs-queue/queues.mdx

To make jobs process more quickly, adjust the `cron` expression in your `autoRun` configuration to run more frequently. Running the job runner more often (e.g., every minute instead of every five minutes) can significantly reduce the latency for job processing, especially for time-sensitive tasks that require prompt execution.

```ts
autoRun: [
  { cron: '* * * * *', limit: 50 } // Run every minute instead of every 5
]
```

