### Query Global Configuration

Source: https://context7.com/payloadcms/payload/llms.txt

Retrieve global configuration data by slug. Globals are site-wide settings like header, footer, or navigation configurations.

```typescript
const header = await sdk.findGlobal({ slug: 'header' })
```

