### Configure Slate Editor in Payload Config

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/packages/richtext-slate/README.md

Initialize and configure the Slate editor in your Payload build configuration. Import the slateEditor function and pass it to the editor property in buildConfig with configuration options.

```typescript
import { buildConfig } from 'payload'
import { slateEditor } from '@payloadcms/richtext-slate'

export default buildConfig({
  editor: slateEditor({}),
  // ...rest of config
})
```
